paragraph.content:
accumulations of dirt and refuse shall be removed daily by a suitable
                    method from the floor and benches of workrooms and from the staircases and
                    passages;

the floor of every workroom shall be cleaned at least once in every week by
                    washing or, if it is effective and suitable, by sweeping or other method;
                    and

in respect of a contravention of
                                                  regulation 16B or 37(1) is
                                                  liable to a fine at level 4;

in respect of failure to make a report or making a false report, as
                    referred to in paragraph (1)(c), is liable to a fine at level 6;
                    or
